/**
 * @title OurMinter
 * @author Nick A.
 * https://github.com/ourz-network/our-contracts
 *
 * These contracts enable creators, builders, & collaborators of all kinds
 * to receive royalties for their collective work, forever.
 *
 * Thank you,
